title: Handshake Medium Dark Skin Tone
description: Two hands meeting in the middle, signifying agreement, greeting, or a deal being made between people with medium-dark skin tones.
apple_vendor_description: The handshake emoji with a medium-dark skin tone, as seen on Apple devices, beautifully captures a moment of agreement and connection. The hands are rendered with realistic texture and lighting, featuring Apple's characteristic glossy sheen and soft, rounded edges. This emoji powerfully symbolizes trust, partnership, collaboration, and the sealing of a deal, conveying a sense of solidarity and mutual respect.
